---

## 🙈 .gitignore

Create a file named `.gitignore` in the exact same directory alongside your `server.js` and `index.html` files, then paste this content inside it:

```text
# Dependency directories
node_modules/
jspm_packages/

# Local development configuration or environment files
.env
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

# IDE configurations and Editor files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# Operating System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Log files
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
logs/
*.log
